Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone beloved to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I first learned what that meant... during the winter when I was fifteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:38.91,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:44.83,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:50.96,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:56.96,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:01:04.35,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:09.02,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:14.94,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:23.87,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:28.79,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:35.88,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:42.68,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:38.91,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:44.83,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:50.96,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:56.96,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:01:04.35,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:09.02,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:14.94,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:23.87,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:28.79,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:35.88,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:42.68,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:58.44,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(140,384)}Episode 6 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:28.46,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Jama da ne te wo futta ushirosugata anna ni mou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:40.97,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuugure no hitonami ni yurenagara chiisaku naru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:51.15,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ga kureta kotoba wo hitotsuzutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:03:02.62,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Omoidashi me wo tojita shiwase na omoi dake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:13.46,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni aru hazu na no ni fuan ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.05,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite na no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:28.46,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in the way, I waved my hand, but your back is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:40.97,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,already swerving through the crowd of people and sinking into the evening sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:51.15,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I closed my eyes and began to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:03:02.62,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,the words you told me. Only happy memories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:13.46,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,are supposed to be there, but I became anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does my...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano embraces me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smoothness of my uniform against my skin feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's hands... touch my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I can feel Yano's masculinity really coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's fingers run through my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving myself so open to him makes my heart clench up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano kisses me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It leaves me so hopeless, unable to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... Yano's hands on my chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a second!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't let me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't stop with just a touch.
