Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:06.45,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H30&\frz17.109\c&H3D4948&\b1\fscx211.25\fscy177.5\move(192,172,200,172,0,610)}Message Sent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I was wrong this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though for a second, I thought it might actually be all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being held tightly by Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of what that version of me would be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I ended up stopping unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm not really sure what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got here before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of this jewelry's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, I can take some out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.21,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz1.515\move(419,443,419,496,0,1025)}Takeuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a beautiful woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... but I may not be buying anything today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with just looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try one on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takaha--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this one's cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're Takeuchi-kun's older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, Takeuchi-kun is always taking good care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a friend of Masahami, I can get you a discount as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy one now! I'm definitely going to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, do you mind if I look around a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't really surprised or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really grown since I last saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend's cute. She seems like a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sorta looks like a baby, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... could I see this one please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, do you think this looks good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, maybe something more childi--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! Just wait here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got these in today, and we haven't even put them on display yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so adorable...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are flower-shaped gems inset into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That definitely would fit someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, then I'll take...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, umm... I think I'll go with the one I was just trying on instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was less expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll go with the other one, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the other one? We only have those sizes 11 and 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too big for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? The one I just had on fit me perfectly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, then I'll take another look around...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be fine. We have many other cute rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're buying it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... could I pay in installments?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money I'll get for New Year and my allowance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then if I sell those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe a deferred payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having the product delivered later, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then hold it until I have enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I did that, you'd never make it in time for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just use my E.D. and get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your E.D.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Employee discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only cost 60% of its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, 40% off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's 40% off, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like this... are really against the rules, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll make this one time a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd damn well better not forget, so bring me all of the money you have on hand by next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate lending money to people in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka-san was really mature and beautiful, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can end up like her if I try really hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... I'm sure you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Takeuchi-kun has such a hard time getting a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like he'd be pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His older sister's too beautiful, so he has higher standards for his dream girl than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now... yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun probably wants a girl more beautiful and mature than his older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said Takeuchi-kun is always taking good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when has he "taken good care of you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... that was just a figure of speech... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just meant as a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I can't believe this is happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all seems so unreal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So unreal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being a bit of a tease about this, Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you're just so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Takeuchi-kun finds a girl soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Takeuchi-kun's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cheer him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then maybe once he gets one, the four of us could go on a double date.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do the four of us have to go somewhere together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if the two of us are alone together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to firmly accept Yano's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You two met?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She treated me really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say this, but... she's really a he, dressed up in female clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... she was really beautiful and so feminine, it surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got you totally fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, calling that guy a male is really an insult to all men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men are more delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I was always the messenger between him and the other guys he was with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally thought you had a sister complex or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop... I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, these people who are all lovey-dovey nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's because he's gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I wouldn't say we're that lovey-dovey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, it's not like you're not popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm not popular that I'm single.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I've been saying, he's a homo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anyone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe it's a sister complex after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:51.09,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\frz20.264\fscx146.25\fscy103.75\frx8\fry358\c&H879493&\move(204,369,186,319,0,3529)}Sorry\N It looks like students\N council meeting's going to\N go over time again, so you\N can leave ahead of me.\N (>_<)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even put a single stick of incense... Pretty heartless, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though half a year's passed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know Onee-chan always had a bad eye for guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... her scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was originally mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would always borrow stuff from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she'd always get it dirty right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She returned one of my favorite T-shirts with a large tomato juice stain on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she make such a big stain, just like a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want it as a memento?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like you're so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She threw you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like you're so much better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sisters, both older and younger, are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...group me with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and end already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about Yano all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's almost time to catch the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Should I just wait for the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that the last time, too. "Just one more hour."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I guess there's no end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home. I'm sure Mom will be worrying, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to kiss one more time before you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, they're all minding their own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting harder and harder to part from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:24.12,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(501,326)\fscx131.25\fscy100\c&H8A8D95&\b1}Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wished that bus would never stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's a limit to how much one person can love another...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.67,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\frz349.514\fscx340\fscy161.25\c&H817A72&\b1\frx14\fry12\pos(299,255)}Sewing Room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san, could you teach me how to do this part?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-san, you have the left and right side reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You loosen it here, and from this part over here, if you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:33.21,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she might hate me since I'm going out with Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and she already hates him so much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it looks like it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really bad at sewing clothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate doing this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san's a little scary with all the stuff she hates...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.71,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\frz349.514\fscx340\fscy161.25\c&H817A72&\b1\frx14\fry12\pos(299,255)}Sewing Room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do in gym today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the food stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get me some milk while you're there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it ruled!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.21,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't group me with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.. yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... not a word of thanks to Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you scraped your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.68,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\b1\fscx222.5\fscy142.5\pos(337,279)\c&H898E8C&\frx4\fry348\frz3.154}Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have to watch out for Yamamoto-san so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem between you and Nana-san is just between you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and her death isn't your fault in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I don't know how to say it--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we're on a bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron. Why are you so quick to say that sort of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And make it a long one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone could come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if we're seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Yano kisses me, I can't think of anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:22:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared of that version of me, but I just can't think of a world without Yano anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it makes me remember all those times, all the way down to the tips of my hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Yano disappeared, I wonder what I'd do...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the person I loved disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the person I loved stopped looking at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always, always stand by my side, Yano.
