Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.39,0:24:22.23,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoigo ni natta youna
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:29.44,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,kodomo mitai nakidashisou
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.44,0:24:36.33,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunao nara konna omoi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.33,0:24:43.00,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,shinakutemo sumu no ni na
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.00,0:24:47.30,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Karappo no watashi dake
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:55.34,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite sakuderu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:25:09.44,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Suki dakara suki dakara zettai suki dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:14.02,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in the way. I waved my hand, but your back is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:26.53,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,already swerving through the crowd of people and sinking into the evening sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:36.21,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I closed my eyes and began to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:47.68,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,the words you told me. Only happy memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:58.52,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,are supposed to be there, but I become anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:08.15,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does my heart waver so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:20.62,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you about my overflowing feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:32.18,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you, I love you, I love you more than anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:49.19,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to turn around, run after you, catch up with you, but
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:24:01.37,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,the sadness of the twilit sky swallowed my courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:10.76,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:17.39,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a short time after we've parted
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.39,0:24:22.23,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cry out like a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:29.44,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,lost child.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.44,0:24:36.33,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could be honest with myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.33,0:24:43.00,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have had to go though this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.00,0:24:47.30,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the empty me is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:55.34,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,here, screaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:25:09.44,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you, I love you, I love you more than anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.99,0:25:35.07,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\fscx97.5\fscy122.5\pos(450,377)}Episode 7 Preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.98,0:25:10.61,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,You only used me to\N get revenge on my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.61,0:25:13.57,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't mean anything, \Nand I'd have no reason to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.57,0:25:16.28,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why did you cry back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.28,0:25:17.62,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cry"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.62,0:25:19.16,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano cried?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.54,0:25:21.58,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:24.42,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.42,0:25:26.96,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...what happened with you and\N Yamamoto-san in middle school?
